Spread fruit ingredients into the bottom of a buttered 3.5 L (13 x 9-inch) pan. In a large microwave safe bowl, heat margarine and marshmallows at HIGH for 3 minutes, stirring after 2 minutes. Stir in vanilla and KELLOGG'S* RICE KRISPIES* cereal until well coated. Using lightly buttered spatula, press into pan on top of fruit mixture. Allow mixture to cool. Cut into squares and serve fruit side up. Best if served the same day.